{Array.from(Array(experienceFormCount).keys()).map((el) => { return (
changeResumeInfo( "experience", "job_title", e.target.value, el ) } required >
changeResumeInfo( "experience", "employeer", e.target.value, el ) } required >
changeResumeInfo( "experience", "location", e.target.value, el ) } required >
changeResumeInfo( "experience", "experience_start_date", e.target.value, el ) } required >
changeResumeInfo( "experience", "experience_end_date", e.target.value, el ) } required >
); })}

); }; export default Experience;
